text: Mustafino () is a rural locality (a village) in Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 73 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Tuymazy, 3 km from Nikolayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Mustafino, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
